              <div class="per">Standalone · cancel anytime</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Weekly Google Business Profile posts written and published</li>
                <li>Citation submissions to top 50 local directories</li>
